<plot>This weekly half hour program is bridging the gap between upcoming film makers and production houses with mainstream television audiences. Successfully pitched as Bill Collins for the MTV audience, The SHORT FILM SHOW screens the hard to find gems created by Australian and international talent from the newest indie film makers to established production houses. The films we play are snappy, enthralling and above all selected for their high entertainment value, making The SHORT FILM SHOW a consistent and reliably enjoying veg-out each week.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?590533</url></doc>
